data.name: LblInfo.Text
data.value: A stylus is a digital pen, which also delivers a pressure value (0% to 100%). This pressure value controls the pen width and can be converted to a Z-value (for a Z axis) or a S-value (for a RC-servo) to control the plotters pen pressure. A mouse delivers a constant pressure value of 50%.
